{"word":"G3670 - ὁμολογέω - homologéō - hom-ol-og-eh'-o - Con- fess","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὁμολογέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">homologéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hom-ol-og-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Con- fess</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சொல், அறிக்கை பண்ணு, வாக்குகொடு, அறிக்கையிடு"},{"paragraph":"1. to say the same thing as another"},{"paragraph":"2. to concede"},{"paragraph":"3. to profess"},{"paragraph":"4. to praise, celebrate"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a compound of the base of <a href=\"#/G3674 - ὁμοῦ - homoû - hom-oo'/3674\">G3674</a> and <a href=\"#/G3056 - λόγος - lógos - log'-os/3056\">G3056</a>; to <i>assent</i>, that is, <i>covenant</i>, <i>acknowledge:</i> - con- (pro-) fess, confession is made, give thanks, promise.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1843/1843\">G1843</a>, <a href=\"#/G3664/3664\">G3664</a>, <a href=\"#/G3665/3665\">G3665</a>, <a href=\"#/G3666/3666\">G3666</a>, <a href=\"#/G3667/3667\">G3667</a>, <a href=\"#/G3668/3668\">G3668</a>, <a href=\"#/G3669/3669\">G3669</a>, <a href=\"#/G3670/3670\">G3670</a>, <a href=\"#/G3671/3671\">G3671</a>, <a href=\"#/G3672/3672\">G3672</a>, <a href=\"#/G3945/3945\">G3945</a>, <a href=\"#/G3946/3946\">G3946</a>, <a href=\"#/G437/437\">G437</a>, <a href=\"#/G871/871\">G871</a>"}]}